Open cmd 
First get the current edition with:

dism /online /get-currentedition

Then get the possible target editions


dism /online /get-targeteditions

Finally set the correct edition (ServerDatacenter or ServerStandard depending on the edition) and type in the product key

dism /online /Set-Edition:ServerDatacenter /productkey:XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX-XXXX /accepteula

REMEMBER that the product key must be in CAPITAL LETTERS or you will get an error

Finally wait a moment until the end of the process. the cmd may hang for a while..

At the end you will get an 'Error 1068' but everything will be fine 

Reboot your machine and voila!

